Company Profile
Sector: Industrials
Industry: Machinery
Sub-Industry: Factory Automation Equipment
Persimmon Technologies Corporation develops and manufactures vacuum robotics. The Company develops Hybrid-Field Motor Technology and produces vacuum robotics for the semiconductor, light emitting diode (LED), organic LED (OLED), solar equipment, and Flat Panel Display (FPD) markets. Persimmon markets its products and services worldwide.




